00428   // hash function. currently only work for string.
00429   size_type _hash_func(const key_type& key) const {
00430     int seed = 1;
00431     int sum = 0;
00432     for (int i=key.length()-1; i>=0; --i) {
00433       int a = key[i];
00434       sum = (sum + (a*seed % table_size)) % table_size;
00435       seed *= 128;
00436     }
00437     // cout << key << " " << sum << endl;
00438     return sum;
00439   }
